title: Billy on the Street- Season 1 (Hector)
description:
This is the whole of Season 1 of Billy on the Street. Like no game show you've ever seen, blending comedy into an eccentric game show, host Eichner runs amuck on the streets of NYC quizzing strangers on music and pop culture for money and prizes.
Hosted by Billy Eichner, where Billy goes out to the streets of New York and asks pedestrians questions about pop culture. Known games are "For A Dollar" and "Quizzed in the Face"
